{"tid":1670702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非常時期]教你點係危急關頭應變 以及日常危機意識","createTime":"2019-10-23T05:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T05:55:14.000Z","uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b27d728a2b0bb8a40d0e799440067202ef153fd8","tid":1670702,"uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QpxUG3osT78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQpxUG3osT78&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=09e9937c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QpxUG3osT78</a><br />\n<br />\n條片講到平時我哋要用咩心態同處理手法應對突發危機，不論天災定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人禍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得入面講到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">訓練日常環境觀察</span></span>同埋真係出現突發危機我哋要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用乜嘢心態同手法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n尤其片中話要deal with一啲有關<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">兇徒</span></span>嘅危機，Run Hide Fight係我幾認同，要好好利用周遭環境保護自己，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>甚至要aggressive過對家</strong></span>先有機會贏<br />\n<br />\n而入面都有啲自制武器 自己參詳下啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"dae2e84cf9930954cdf52f5b8050a79df665b799","tid":1670702,"uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"008d711c212f53d9f97813ca3318b87a199c7719","tid":1670702,"uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"213ee4237fd7482fcd4b6265a405747e5ada3214","tid":1670702,"uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"日常訓練都好重要<br />\n要練習短時間分析大量資訊<br />\n記憶力尤關重要"},{"pid":"46c9a4f2f9962fbcad607331295c777d97272563","tid":1670702,"uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":